# C++ Project on Replit

## Overview
This is a C++ project set up for learning and development on Replit.

## Setup
- Language: C++ (Clang 14)
- Standard: C++17
- Compiler: clang++

## How to Use
1. Write your C++ code in `main.cpp` or create new .cpp files
2. Click the "Run" button at the top to compile and run your program
3. The program will automatically compile and execute

## Current State
- Basic Hello World program is set up in `main.cpp`
- Workflow configured to compile with C++17 standard

